      p We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.

      h2 Changes to This Privacy Policy
      p We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Please review it periodically for any changes. Your continued use of our website constitutes your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.
